---
title: Tofu and Zucchini Rigatoni with Parmesan Blush Sauce
description: This creamy, tomato-based blush sauce with crumbled tofu and tender zucchini makes a perfect light, tasty pasta. This dish comes together quickly and is brightened up with a touch of fresh herbs!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/rigatonis-au-tofu-et-aux-courgettes-61dbb78e.jpg
